{
  "stem": "8947.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had-- we had to-- very primitive conditions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to wash ourselves and the laundry with salt water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we left Cyprus, you know, we could tear up all our clothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were guarded by the British.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if you tried-- you know, we could see sometimes ships coming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you tried to swim out, they would shoot you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, they could-- they-- they would-- you could not escape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, what happened, you know, while independence, the war was going on, they needed-- Like Dr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Ashkenazi was taken out from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know how they did it, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They needed some specialists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I think that was the Jewish underground who was doing that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, things happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some physicians were taken out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But my husband was a very young physician, and they had-- they needed those in the camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, I-- I learned to live with the sea and its moods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I love the sea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I have seen its beauty and also its cruelty, in some ways.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The first-- first time my husband erected a tent, it came a big storm, and the tent was getting up, and we got all wet.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But you know, there were very many people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when you have many people, our food was-- was-- was very poor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We had this half of-- I told you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But for instance, entertainment, there were people who were boxing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were boxing matches, you know, and things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was a hard life, and the hardest part was that we didn't know what's going to happen to us, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I was on night duty as  a nurse, and then if somebody came and needed a doctor, I went with the gas light, you know, in the camps.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
